question.title: Site not rendering because of NoSuchMethodError
question.body:
Having a pom.xml like this:

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<project xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0"
    xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
    xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/maven-v4_0_0.xsd">
    <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>
    <groupId>a</groupId>
    <artifactId>a</artifactId>
    <version>1.0.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
    <packaging>jar</packaging>
    <name>a</name>
    <build>
        <defaultGoal>clean install javadoc:javadoc test site lesscss:compile</defaultGoal>
        <plugins>
            <plugin>
                <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
                <artifactId>maven-site-plugin</artifactId>
                <version>3.21.0</version>
                <dependencies>
                    <dependency>
                        <groupId>org.asciidoctor</groupId>
                        <artifactId>asciidoctor-parser-doxia-module</artifactId>
                        <version>3.0.0</version>
                    </dependency>
                </dependencies>
            </plugin>
        </plugins>
    </build>
</project>

A asciidoc like this (/src/site/asciidoc/a.adoc):

= Hi

And site.xml like this (/src/site/site.xml):

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<project xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
    xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/DECORATION/1.6.0"
    xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/DECORATION/1.6.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/decoration-1.6.0.xsd">
    <skin>
        <groupId>org.apache.maven.skins</groupId>
        <artifactId>maven-fluido-skin</artifactId>
        <version>2.0.0</version>
    </skin>
</project>
